WEBVTT

00:04.720 --> 00:06.680
(BIRDSONG)

00:08.000 --> 00:14.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:15.040 --> 00:17.040
(GALLOPING HOOVES)

00:29.080 --> 00:30.800
<font color="#00ffff">Yah! Yah!</font>

00:38.000 --> 00:39.600
(HORSE WHINNIES)

00:47.600 --> 00:49.400
(POUNDING ON DOOR)

01:05.280 --> 01:08.360
<font color="#00ff00">Begging your pardon, ma'am,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the messenger from Windsor is here.</font>

01:09.720 --> 01:12.520
<font color="#00ff00">He has a black armband on his right</font>
<font color="#00ff00">arm.</font>

01:15.360 --> 01:16.560
You are the first to know.

01:21.360 --> 01:23.200
<font color="#ffff00">And no-one else knows?</font>

01:23.240 --> 01:25.680
<font color="#00ffff">I came straight to you,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Sir John, as instructed.</font>

01:25.720 --> 01:28.360
<font color="#ffff00">Good man. I must get to work.</font>

01:30.680 --> 01:33.760
<font color="#ffff00">And I suggest</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you smarten yourself up.</font>

01:33.800 --> 01:36.960
<font color="#ffff00">You are Steward</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of the Queen's Household now.</font>

01:48.000 --> 01:49.600
(KNOCKING)

01:57.120 --> 01:58.840
<font color="#ffff00">The messenger's here.</font>

01:58.880 --> 02:00.680
<font color="#ffff00">With a black armband,</font>

02:00.720 --> 02:02.800
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty.</font>

02:15.520 --> 02:16.760
(DOG YAPS)

02:19.040 --> 02:20.880
I can manage, Lehzen.

02:20.920 --> 02:22.200
Alone.

02:28.840 --> 02:30.040
(DOG BARKS)

02:38.480 --> 02:43.960
It is my sad duty to inform you that
the King breathed his last at twelve
minutes past two.

02:44.000 --> 02:46.000
My poor dear uncle.
(BARKING)

02:46.080 --> 02:47.600
May God have mercy on his soul.

02:52.680 --> 02:53.840
Your Majesty.

02:56.760 --> 02:58.440
Naughty Dashy.

03:01.040 --> 03:06.440
# Gloriana

03:07.040 --> 03:12.600
# Hallelujah

03:13.440 --> 03:19.440
# Gloriana

03:19.480 --> 03:22.840
# Hallelujah

03:26.120 --> 03:31.800
# Gloriana, hallelujah

03:32.280 --> 03:37.480
# Hallelujah! #

04:07.400 --> 04:09.000
Prime Minister?

04:11.440 --> 04:12.800
<font color="#ffff00">The King?</font>

04:16.279 --> 04:18.200
<font color="#ffff00">Coffee.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">BUTLER: Yes, sir.</font>

04:22.480 --> 04:23.840
<font color="#00ff00">Drina, was ist...</font>

04:25.800 --> 04:28.400
<font color="#00ffff">Der Konig?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, Mama.</font>

04:30.040 --> 04:31.400
<font color="#00ffff">Mein liebling.</font>

04:31.440 --> 04:34.200
<font color="#00ffff">Mein kleines Madchen is the Queen.</font>

04:36.440 --> 04:38.280
No more German, Mama.

04:39.480 --> 04:42.880
You must remember you are the mother
of the Queen of England now.

04:43.640 --> 04:45.360
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, Sir John.</font>

04:45.400 --> 04:49.160
<font color="#00ffff">That awful old man is dead</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and now little Drina is Queen.</font>

04:50.280 --> 04:55.040
<font color="#00ff00">So, I suppose the first thing to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">decide is how you will style</font>
<font color="#00ff00">yourself.</font>

04:55.080 --> 04:56.960
<font color="#00ff00">Alexandrina, that's too foreign,</font>

04:57.000 --> 04:59.320
<font color="#00ff00">and Victoria is hardly the name for</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a queen.</font>

04:59.360 --> 05:04.040
We need something more traditional,
like Elizabeth perhaps, or Anne.

05:04.080 --> 05:06.920
<font color="#00ff00">I think Elizabeth II</font>
<font color="#00ff00">sounds very well.</font>

05:08.840 --> 05:10.320
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty.</font>

05:10.360 --> 05:14.760
<font color="#00ff00">Lady Flora, don't you think</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Elizabeth would be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">an excellent name?</font>

05:14.800 --> 05:17.800
<font color="#ffff00">A reminder of a great queen.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Yes.</font>

05:17.840 --> 05:21.240
<font color="#00ffff">Has the Archbishop come?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">We must not keep him waiting.</font>

05:21.280 --> 05:23.320
Actually, the Archbishop has already
left.

05:24.640 --> 05:26.000
<font color="#00ff00">You saw him on your own?</font>

05:28.800 --> 05:31.280
I intend to see all my ministers
alone.

05:31.320 --> 05:34.080
<font color="#00ff00">This is not a game!</font>

05:35.520 --> 05:37.480
<font color="#00ff00">In future...</font>

05:39.560 --> 05:44.000
..you must be accompanied
by your mother or me.

06:04.080 --> 06:06.080
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

06:16.320 --> 06:17.800
<font color="#00ff00">William, do stop for a moment.</font>

06:19.000 --> 06:20.840
Is it true the King is dead?

06:20.880 --> 06:24.720
<font color="#ffff00">I am on my way now to Kensington</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to kiss hands with the new Queen.</font>

06:24.760 --> 06:27.480
<font color="#00ffff">I hear her tongue is too big for her</font>
<font color="#00ffff">mouth.</font>

06:27.520 --> 06:31.000
<font color="#00ff00">Nonsense, I have seen the Queen</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and she is perfectly formed.</font>

06:31.040 --> 06:34.920
<font color="#00ff00">So, William, why the long face?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, I'm tired of governing.</font>

06:34.960 --> 06:39.640
<font color="#ffff00">I wish I could just retire</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to Brocket Hall</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and contemplate the rooks.</font>

06:39.680 --> 06:41.440
<font color="#00ff00">The rooks must wait.</font>

06:41.480 --> 06:44.720
<font color="#00ff00">Your queen needs you, your party</font>
<font color="#00ff00">needs you,</font>

06:44.760 --> 06:47.920
<font color="#00ff00">and I would very much like a place</font>
<font color="#00ff00">at court.</font>

06:47.960 --> 06:52.360
In that case, Emma, I say I have no
choice but to shoulder my burden.

06:52.400 --> 06:53.800
<font color="#ffff00">Good day.</font>

07:03.880 --> 07:07.800
I think it's a little late for
Blackstone's commentaries now,
Lehzen.

07:07.840 --> 07:10.880
<font color="#ffff00">We haven't got very far with our</font>
<font color="#ffff00">studies of the constitution.</font>

07:10.920 --> 07:13.200
I'll just have to do the best I can.

07:16.400 --> 07:19.120
<font color="#ffff00">I suppose I shall be returning to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Hanover.</font>

07:19.160 --> 07:21.360
<font color="#ffff00">You are not needing a governess now.</font>

07:21.400 --> 07:25.480
Dearest Lehzen,
someone has to run my household,

07:25.520 --> 07:27.600
the way I would like it.

07:35.760 --> 07:37.400
<font color="#ffff00">The Queen wants all her things</font>

07:37.440 --> 07:39.280
<font color="#ffff00">moved into the blue state room</font>
<font color="#ffff00">tonight.</font>

07:39.320 --> 07:41.440
<font color="#ffff00">She will be sleeping there</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from now on.</font>

07:43.920 --> 07:46.560
<font color="#00ffff">I will have to talk to Sir John</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about that.</font>

07:49.640 --> 07:51.160
<font color="#ffff00">No, Mr Penge, you will not.</font>

07:51.200 --> 07:54.480
The Queen has put me in charge
of the Royal Household.

07:55.520 --> 07:57.720
I congratulate you, Baroness.

07:58.720 --> 08:00.160
<font color="#ffff00">I warn you, Mr Penge.</font>

08:01.280 --> 08:05.320
I intend to run this household
according to modern principles of
economy.

08:05.360 --> 08:07.320
I will want to see all the accounts,

08:07.360 --> 08:10.720
and that includes the Dressers'
Book, Mrs Jenkins.

08:11.760 --> 08:14.200
<font color="#ffff00">I will have no patience with</font>
<font color="#ffff00">extravagance.</font>

08:20.120 --> 08:23.360
<font color="#00ffff">So now we are answerable to a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">governess.</font>

08:23.400 --> 08:25.440
And a German one at that!

08:25.480 --> 08:27.120
<font color="#00ffff">God save the Queen.</font>

08:27.160 --> 08:29.200
And all who work for her.

08:41.240 --> 08:44.520
<font color="#00ff00">Prime Minister,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a moment of your time.</font>

08:45.320 --> 08:49.000
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen has led</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the most sheltered life until now</font>

08:49.040 --> 08:52.200
<font color="#00ff00">and her mother is concerned</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that she should not be overburdened.</font>

08:57.400 --> 08:59.600
<font color="#00ff00">As her mother's trusted advisor,</font>

08:59.640 --> 09:02.880
<font color="#00ff00">if I were to act as the Queen's</font>
<font color="#00ff00">private secretary,</font>

09:02.920 --> 09:06.880
<font color="#00ff00">you could be sure that your</font>
<font color="#00ff00">interests would be served most</font>
<font color="#00ff00">faithfully.</font>

09:07.720 --> 09:10.920
<font color="#ffff00">Well, thank you, Sir John.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I shall bear that in mind.</font>

09:14.240 --> 09:15.800
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Melbourne is here.</font>

09:15.840 --> 09:18.840
Perhaps I should stay as chaperone.

09:18.880 --> 09:21.760
No, a monarch always meets the prime
minister alone.

09:21.800 --> 09:24.160
<font color="#ffff00">Drina, I mean, Majesty...</font>

09:26.320 --> 09:28.840
<font color="#ffff00">..I have always tried to shield you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from these things,</font>

09:28.880 --> 09:31.280
but Lord Melbourne, I'm afraid, is
disreputable!

09:31.320 --> 09:34.240
Nevertheless, I will meet him alone.

09:46.440 --> 09:47.920
<font color="#ffff00">You may go in now.</font>

10:03.120 --> 10:06.920
<font color="#ffff00">May I offer you my condolences</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on the death of your uncle, Your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Majesty.</font>

10:06.960 --> 10:08.840
He was always kind to me.

10:10.760 --> 10:13.760
Though he did have some strange
ideas about who I should marry.

10:15.360 --> 10:17.440
<font color="#ffff00">I believe he favoured the Prince</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of Orange.</font>

10:17.480 --> 10:19.480
A prince with a head
the size of a pumpkin.

10:20.760 --> 10:23.080
I see you have a keen eye for
detail, Ma'am.

10:27.560 --> 10:28.920
<font color="#ffff00">May I?</font>

10:33.120 --> 10:35.800
<font color="#ffff00">What's her name?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">She doesn't have a name.</font>

10:36.840 --> 10:38.520
She's number 123.

10:39.520 --> 10:41.880
My mother gave her to me
on my 11th birthday.

10:42.840 --> 10:45.000
<font color="#ffff00">With the crown?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">That came later.</font>

10:46.120 --> 10:48.880
I made it for her on the day I
realised I would be queen.

10:52.320 --> 10:54.000
<font color="#ffff00">When was that?</font>

10:55.920 --> 10:57.280
I was 13.

10:58.440 --> 11:02.480
I was having a history lesson with
Lehzen. She showed me the family tree

11:02.520 --> 11:04.560
and I looked at it for a long time.

11:05.720 --> 11:08.080
And then I realised I was next.

11:08.120 --> 11:10.080
<font color="#ffff00">Were you pleased?</font>

11:10.120 --> 11:13.080
I remember thinking my uncle's crown
would be too big for me.

11:18.360 --> 11:22.040
I believe you are acquainted with
my mother's advisor,
Sir John Conroy.

11:22.080 --> 11:27.440
<font color="#ffff00">I have met him, Ma'am. I would not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">say we were acquaintances.</font>

11:28.400 --> 11:30.600
<font color="#ffff00">He would like to be your private</font>
<font color="#ffff00">secretary.</font>

11:30.640 --> 11:32.520
That is out of the question.

11:34.560 --> 11:38.160
<font color="#ffff00">I see. </font><font color="#ffffff"> He means to run me, as he</font>
runs my mother.

11:38.920 --> 11:40.680
<font color="#ffff00">Well, then, you must have someone</font>
<font color="#ffff00">else.</font>

11:43.280 --> 11:45.720
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps I might act for you.</font>

11:45.760 --> 11:48.560
There's a great deal of business
that needs to be attended to.

11:48.600 --> 11:51.200
<font color="#ffff00">The despatch boxes are probably</font>
<font color="#ffff00">already on their way to you</font>

11:51.240 --> 11:53.040
with documents that require your
signature.

11:53.080 --> 11:54.960
<font color="#ffff00">Tomorrow is the Privy Council.</font>

11:55.000 --> 11:59.320
Thank you, Lord Melbourne,
but when I require assistance,
I will ask for it.

12:00.600 --> 12:02.160
<font color="#ffff00">In that case, Ma'am.</font>

12:10.400 --> 12:12.400
(BELL TOLLS)

12:14.760 --> 12:16.520
(DOG BARKS)

12:16.560 --> 12:19.280
<font color="#00ffff">You are going to Kensington Palace?</font>

12:19.320 --> 12:22.480
<font color="#00ff00">To swear allegiance to my niece.</font>

12:22.520 --> 12:26.920
<font color="#00ffff">She is very young and rather</font>
<font color="#00ffff">delicate.</font>

12:26.960 --> 12:31.760
<font color="#00ffff">Now your foolish brother is dead,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">if anything should happen to her,</font>

12:31.800 --> 12:34.280
you are the heir to the throne.

12:35.600 --> 12:37.880
(CHATTER)

12:42.520 --> 12:43.960
<font color="#00ff00">Gentlemen.</font>

12:45.200 --> 12:46.880
<font color="#00ff00">Shall we?</font>

13:10.320 --> 13:11.600
(EXHALES)

13:11.640 --> 13:13.640
(CHATTER)

13:15.320 --> 13:17.320
(SILENCE FALLS)

13:18.800 --> 13:20.400
(DOOR CLOSES)

13:35.800 --> 13:37.240
My Lords...

13:38.840 --> 13:43.560
..now that it has pleased Almighty
God to call to his mercy my uncle...

13:43.600 --> 13:45.440
<font color="#00ff00">Can't hear you.</font>

13:53.280 --> 13:55.400
I know that I'm young.

13:56.920 --> 14:00.640
And some would say
my sex puts me at a disadvantage.

14:02.120 --> 14:04.320
But I know my duty,

14:04.360 --> 14:06.920
and I assure you I am ready

14:06.960 --> 14:10.640
for the great responsibility that
lies before me.

14:19.880 --> 14:21.800
<font color="#00ff00">Your Majesty.</font>

14:33.800 --> 14:35.600
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Ilchester.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Lord Ilchester.</font>

14:39.640 --> 14:41.880
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Howard.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Your Majesty.</font>

14:43.080 --> 14:45.520
Lord Howard.
<font color="#00ff00">Your Majesty.</font>

14:45.560 --> 14:48.080
<font color="#ffff00">Viscount Falkland.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Viscount Falkland.</font>

14:48.120 --> 14:49.600
Lord Shaftesbury.

14:49.640 --> 14:52.320
<font color="#00ff00">Your Majesty.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Lord Fitzroy.</font>

14:56.120 --> 14:58.200
<font color="#ffff00">I believe you know this one.</font>

14:59.200 --> 15:01.880
<font color="#00ff00">Your Majesty.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Uncle Cumberland.</font>

15:05.200 --> 15:08.600
When will you be going to Hanover?
<font color="#00ff00">I am in no hurry.</font>

15:08.640 --> 15:11.360
My first loyalty is to the British
throne.

15:13.600 --> 15:16.320
I'm sure the people of Hanover
will be sorry to hear that.

15:17.200 --> 15:19.440
<font color="#ffff00">I believe there's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">quite a crowd outside</font>

15:19.480 --> 15:21.560
<font color="#ffff00">waiting to hear the proclamation.</font>

15:21.600 --> 15:24.720
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps now would be a good time</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to show yourself on the balcony.</font>

15:43.560 --> 15:45.280
In the proclamation,

15:45.320 --> 15:47.320
I am referred to
as Alexandrina Victoria.

15:47.360 --> 15:49.840
But I do not like the name
Alexandrina.

15:51.960 --> 15:53.600
From now on...

15:53.640 --> 15:57.120
I wish to be called...Victoria.

15:58.800 --> 16:00.600
<font color="#ffff00">Queen Victoria.</font>

16:13.000 --> 16:15.000
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

16:35.120 --> 16:37.120
(CHATTER IN GERMAN)

16:41.400 --> 16:43.200
<font color="#ffff00">This is Miss Skerrett.</font>

16:43.240 --> 16:46.080
<font color="#ffff00">She is to work with you,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Mrs Jenkins, as a dresser.</font>

16:46.120 --> 16:48.720
But the senior dresser always
chooses her own assistants.

16:48.760 --> 16:51.680
I've already made enquiries.
<font color="#ffff00">I've saved you the trouble.</font>

16:51.720 --> 16:54.840
<font color="#ffff00">Miss Skerrett was a pupil</font>
<font color="#ffff00">at the Chiswick Institute</font>

16:54.880 --> 16:57.320
and has come highly recommended
by the principal.

16:57.360 --> 17:01.160
<font color="#00ffff">I'm sure Mrs Jenkins</font>
<font color="#00ffff">will be very grateful for the help.</font>

17:05.440 --> 17:07.560
Highly recommended, is it?

17:07.599 --> 17:10.599
Aren't we the lucky ones? What is it
they taught you there, hm?

17:10.640 --> 17:13.960
Astronomy? The pianoforte? French?

17:14.000 --> 17:16.800
<font color="#00ffff">Some French, ma'am,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but mostly needlework,</font>

17:16.839 --> 17:19.200
<font color="#00ffff">and how to make myself useful.</font>

17:19.240 --> 17:22.599
At least you're English.
There's enough Germans at the palace.

17:22.640 --> 17:24.520
<font color="#00ffff">Pumpernickel Palace.</font>

17:38.080 --> 17:40.160
I will do my best, Papa.

17:40.200 --> 17:41.800
(DOOR OPENS)

17:43.600 --> 17:45.840
<font color="#00ff00">Still playing with dolls,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Your Royal Highness?</font>

17:45.880 --> 17:50.680
<font color="#00ff00">Forgive me. Still playing with</font>
<font color="#00ff00">dolls, Your Majesty?</font>

17:53.440 --> 17:55.440
<font color="#00ff00">You must look over the letters</font>
<font color="#00ff00">patent.</font>

17:56.640 --> 17:59.800
There are still so many decisions to
be made.

18:01.080 --> 18:03.720
<font color="#00ff00">And I believe there are several</font>
<font color="#00ff00">bishoprics to be filled.</font>

18:03.760 --> 18:05.880
I think, Sir John,
now that I'm queen,

18:05.920 --> 18:08.320
I do not need your assistance.
Thank you.

18:12.880 --> 18:14.080
<font color="#00ff00">What?</font>

18:16.440 --> 18:18.840
<font color="#00ff00">Do you really imagine</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that you can step</font>

18:18.880 --> 18:22.880
<font color="#00ff00">from the schoolroom straight to the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">throne without guidance?</font>

18:24.200 --> 18:26.920
<font color="#00ff00">Do you have any idea of what is at</font>
<font color="#00ff00">stake here?</font>

18:26.960 --> 18:28.760
I'd have been better prepared

18:28.800 --> 18:30.840
if you'd allowed me
to go out into society

18:30.880 --> 18:33.640
instead of keeping me here
at Kensington all the time.

18:35.080 --> 18:36.880
I know my duty is to serve my
country.

18:38.000 --> 18:40.520
Mama, you know I'm ready.

18:40.560 --> 18:44.120
I want so much to make you and poor
dear Papa proud.

18:48.720 --> 18:52.280
<font color="#00ff00">What can a girl like you,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">unformed...</font>

18:53.480 --> 18:55.720
..possibly do to serve her country?

18:57.040 --> 18:58.880
<font color="#00ff00">No.</font>

18:58.920 --> 19:01.920
You must take advice.

19:01.960 --> 19:04.600
<font color="#00ffff">And we must be your shepherds.</font>

19:06.920 --> 19:08.640
I think you forget.

19:10.840 --> 19:13.400
Although I am young, and perhaps
ignorant...

19:14.760 --> 19:16.960
..I am my father's daughter...

19:18.200 --> 19:19.920
..the granddaughter of a king,

19:19.960 --> 19:21.680
and I believe I shall find my own
way.

19:21.720 --> 19:24.080
And if I require advice,
I will ask for it.

19:27.800 --> 19:31.320
Sir John, you have our permission to
withdraw.

19:46.160 --> 19:49.040
<font color="#00ffff">Drina. Please, Drina.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(DOOR CLOSES)</font>

19:50.160 --> 19:51.480
<font color="#00ffff">Sir John is your friend.</font>

19:51.520 --> 19:56.000
No, Mama. He has always been your
friend, not mine.

19:58.400 --> 20:02.000
I'm surprised they didn't teach you
how to do this at your institute.

20:02.040 --> 20:04.120
<font color="#00ffff">Think that's taken, Mrs Jenkins?</font>

20:04.160 --> 20:06.600
I hope you realise how lucky you are
to be here.

20:06.640 --> 20:08.680
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, this is exactly the kind of life</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I want.</font>

20:16.120 --> 20:18.640
<font color="#00ffff">I am very good at mending,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Mrs Jenkins.</font>

20:18.680 --> 20:20.880
Would you like me to see
what I can do with these?

20:20.920 --> 20:24.680
Oh, the Queen won't wear mended
gloves, she has a fresh pair every
time she goes out.

20:24.720 --> 20:29.200
But she does wear mended stockings,
so you can show me how clever you
are with those.

20:31.920 --> 20:34.960
<font color="#00ffff">Drina is so...</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know how to say in English.</font>

20:35.000 --> 20:37.880
<font color="#00ff00">Stubborn. She has always been</font>
<font color="#00ff00">stubborn.</font>

20:37.920 --> 20:40.000
I think we should move at once.

20:40.040 --> 20:43.480
Flora Hastings actually came into my
closet unannounced this morning.

20:43.520 --> 20:45.840
She's Mama's lady-in-waiting, not
mine.

20:46.880 --> 20:51.040
And that man was in the library
when I came down to look at
newspapers.

20:51.080 --> 20:54.080
<font color="#00ff00">She will soon realise that she is</font>
<font color="#00ff00">out of her depth,</font>

20:54.120 --> 20:56.880
<font color="#00ff00">with only the Baroness</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to run things for her.</font>

20:56.920 --> 20:59.200
I cannot live like this any longer.

20:59.240 --> 21:01.960
<font color="#ffff00">You would be quite separate</font>
<font color="#ffff00">at Buckingham House.</font>

21:03.040 --> 21:04.280
Yes.

21:09.920 --> 21:11.760
Don't take less than five shillings.

21:11.800 --> 21:14.240
<font color="#00ff00">Have I ever let you down before,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Mrs Jenkins?</font>

21:14.280 --> 21:15.760
Go on, off you go.

21:20.480 --> 21:24.840
<font color="#00ffff">That parcel Mrs Jenkins gave you.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Where are you taking it?</font>

21:24.880 --> 21:26.840
<font color="#00ff00">To the pickers, of course.</font>

21:26.880 --> 21:29.400
<font color="#00ff00">It's the second parcel this week</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I've taken.</font>

21:29.440 --> 21:32.440
<font color="#00ffff">Mrs Jenkins does well from the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">pickers? </font><font color="#00ff00"> Oh, yes.</font>

21:32.480 --> 21:34.520
<font color="#00ff00">Five shillings for a pair of gloves,</font>

21:34.560 --> 21:36.880
<font color="#00ff00">and she once got three guineas for</font>
<font color="#00ff00">shoes.</font>

21:36.920 --> 21:40.160
She always gives me a sixpence
for running them down for her.

21:40.200 --> 21:43.440
<font color="#00ff00">Don't worry, Miss Skerrett,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you'll find your own perk right</font>
<font color="#00ff00">enough.</font>

21:43.480 --> 21:45.720
<font color="#00ffff">Thank you for setting me straight,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Brodie.</font>

21:47.000 --> 21:50.720
<font color="#00ffff">I don't understand why Drina</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is in such a hurry to move.</font>

21:50.760 --> 21:52.840
<font color="#00ffff">We have been so happy here at</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Kensington.</font>

21:52.880 --> 21:54.920
<font color="#ffff00">She is so young, Ma'am.</font>

21:54.960 --> 21:57.680
<font color="#ffff00">For her, the bustle of the city will</font>
<font color="#ffff00">be a novelty.</font>

21:57.720 --> 22:00.760
<font color="#00ff00">And for you, Ma'am, it will be an</font>
<font color="#00ff00">opportunity.</font>

22:00.800 --> 22:03.200
At Buckingham House,
you will be Queen Mother.

22:03.240 --> 22:05.720
<font color="#00ffff">And you will be her private</font>
<font color="#00ffff">secretary.</font>

22:05.760 --> 22:08.160
<font color="#00ff00">I wish I could be sure of that.</font>

22:21.120 --> 22:23.600
<font color="#ffff00">The carriage is waiting, Majesty.</font>

22:47.800 --> 22:52.160
So many windows. <font color="#ffff00">They almost</font>
<font color="#ffff00">bankrupted your uncle George.</font>

22:53.400 --> 22:55.600
How light it will be after
Kensington.

22:55.640 --> 22:57.920
<font color="#ffff00">Did you find it so very dark there?</font>

22:59.200 --> 23:00.920
It was hard to see things clearly.

23:12.000 --> 23:14.000
Oh, I think this will do quite well.

23:53.160 --> 23:57.960
<font color="#ffff00">Yes. I think before your first</font>
<font color="#ffff00">levee, we should probably try to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">find a throne that fits.</font>

23:58.000 --> 24:01.600
It is hard to be dignified
when your feet are six inches
from the floor.

24:04.360 --> 24:08.960
You see, I don't understand why this
place is called a house not a palace.

24:09.920 --> 24:12.240
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you can call it whatever you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">like, Ma'am.</font>

24:13.960 --> 24:15.760
<font color="#00ff00">You could get lost in here.</font>

24:15.800 --> 24:19.680
This is what I call a royal
residence.

24:31.680 --> 24:34.400
She is small.
But she ain't no midget.

24:34.440 --> 24:37.120
<font color="#00ff00">No. Everything is in proportion.</font>

24:39.840 --> 24:42.680
At least here I'll be completely
separate from Mama.

24:42.720 --> 24:46.440
I cannot have Sir John
hovering about me all the time.

24:46.480 --> 24:50.760
<font color="#ffff00">I believe the Duchess</font>
<font color="#ffff00">relies on Conroy a good deal.</font>

24:50.800 --> 24:53.360
He's been handling her affairs for
some time.

24:53.400 --> 24:56.080
They all think because I'm small
that I'm still a child.

24:56.120 --> 24:59.040
They've always underestimated me.
They expect me to fail.

25:01.840 --> 25:04.280
They don't believe me capable of
being Queen.

25:05.000 --> 25:07.280
<font color="#ffff00">I think they're mistaken, Ma'am.</font>

25:08.760 --> 25:11.080
<font color="#ffff00">And anyone who dares comment</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on your stature</font>

25:11.120 --> 25:13.080
<font color="#ffff00">should be sent</font>
<font color="#ffff00">straight to the Tower.</font>

25:13.120 --> 25:15.480
<font color="#ffff00">I've only known you a short while,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am,</font>

25:15.520 --> 25:19.720
<font color="#ffff00">but I'm confident that you will</font>
<font color="#ffff00">bring great credit to the monarchy.</font>

25:19.760 --> 25:22.440
<font color="#ffff00">It's true your education may be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">lacking in some areas,</font>

25:22.480 --> 25:25.200
but you have a natural dignity
that cannot be learnt.

25:25.920 --> 25:28.240
You don't think I'm too short to be
dignified?

25:28.280 --> 25:31.480
<font color="#ffff00">To me, Ma'am, you are every inch a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">queen.</font>

25:34.360 --> 25:36.520
Lord Melbourne, when we first met,

25:36.560 --> 25:39.240
you offered to act as
my private secretary.

25:40.520 --> 25:43.400
<font color="#ffff00">You did not accept my offer.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">But you are still willing?</font>

25:45.360 --> 25:47.200
<font color="#ffff00">I would be honoured, Ma'am.</font>

25:49.000 --> 25:50.640
Thank you...

25:51.800 --> 25:53.480
..Lord M.

26:04.520 --> 26:08.080
<font color="#ffff00">How are you finding the north wing,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Your Royal Highness?</font>

26:08.120 --> 26:11.520
<font color="#00ffff">Where are my daughter's rooms?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">In the south wing, Ma'am.</font>

26:12.960 --> 26:14.880
<font color="#00ffff">And where do you sleep, Baroness?</font>

26:14.920 --> 26:18.640
<font color="#ffff00">I have a room next to the Queen,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with an interconnecting door.</font>

26:20.360 --> 26:21.600
<font color="#00ffff">I see.</font>

26:25.440 --> 26:27.240
<font color="#00ffff">The north wing.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I know.</font>

26:28.200 --> 26:29.760
<font color="#00ffff">This is...</font>

26:29.800 --> 26:31.120
<font color="#00ff00">Duchess?</font>

26:32.280 --> 26:33.840
<font color="#00ff00">Ma'am.</font>

26:35.200 --> 26:38.680
<font color="#00ffff">Well, I think I should go back to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Coburg.</font>

26:39.560 --> 26:42.440
<font color="#00ff00">Forgive me, Duchess,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but you should do no such thing.</font>

26:42.480 --> 26:44.800
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen will falter,</font>

26:44.840 --> 26:48.720
<font color="#00ff00">and when she does, you must be on</font>
<font color="#00ff00">hand to guide her and show the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">country</font>

26:48.760 --> 26:51.720
<font color="#00ff00">that even if the daughter is</font>
<font color="#00ff00">foolish, the mother is not.</font>

26:51.760 --> 26:56.600
<font color="#00ffff">You're right. I'm not a...flib,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">flib...?</font>

26:56.640 --> 26:59.160
<font color="#ffff00">Flibbertigibbet?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Mama?</font>

27:00.320 --> 27:02.840
I came to see how you've settled in.

27:02.880 --> 27:05.200
<font color="#00ffff">So kind of you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to come such a long way.</font>

27:05.240 --> 27:07.520
<font color="#00ff00">Now that you are established</font>
<font color="#00ff00">here, Ma'am,</font>

27:07.560 --> 27:09.560
<font color="#00ff00">it is time that</font>
<font color="#00ff00">we chose your ladies.</font>

27:09.600 --> 27:11.680
It is vital to set the right tone.

27:11.720 --> 27:15.560
<font color="#ffff00">I have drawn up a list</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of reliable maids of honour, Ma'am,</font>

27:15.600 --> 27:17.400
none of them above average height.

27:20.000 --> 27:22.840
Good day, Mama. I hope you'll find
it comfortable here.

27:24.760 --> 27:26.080
<font color="#00ff00">Ma'am!</font>

27:27.440 --> 27:30.080
<font color="#ffff00">I urge you to look at my list,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>

27:30.120 --> 27:32.480
Don't make any mistakes
with your maids of honour.

27:32.520 --> 27:36.360
<font color="#ffff00">Young girls can be so flighty.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Really?</font>

27:36.400 --> 27:39.400
<font color="#ffff00">You cannot be too careful</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with these appointments.</font>

27:39.440 --> 27:42.040
They set the tone for the whole
court.

27:42.080 --> 27:45.400
Please allow me to serve you in any
way I can.

27:45.440 --> 27:47.920
I will bear that in mind,
Lady Flora.

27:58.320 --> 28:02.120
<font color="#00ffff">Careful, boy! The pickers won't</font>
<font color="#00ffff">take them if they're broken.</font>

28:03.680 --> 28:06.360
<font color="#00ff00">Still, you'll be doing all right for</font>
<font color="#00ff00">yourself, Mr Penge.</font>

28:06.400 --> 28:09.680
There's over 1,000 candles a week
in this corridor alone.

28:09.720 --> 28:13.520
<font color="#00ff00">Don't suppose there's an extra</font>
<font color="#00ff00">shilling in it for me,</font>

28:13.560 --> 28:16.240
<font color="#00ff00">you know, for running 'em down to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the pickers?</font>

28:17.960 --> 28:21.160
<font color="#00ff00">Sixpence?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You're learning boy. Nice try.</font>

28:23.000 --> 28:25.320
<font color="#00ff00">We usually change</font>
<font color="#00ff00">around three times a day.</font>

28:25.360 --> 28:28.080
<font color="#00ff00">More, of course,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">if we've being out riding.</font>

28:29.160 --> 28:33.360
<font color="#ffff00">This is Skerrett, Majesty.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">From the institute at Chiswick.</font>

28:33.400 --> 28:34.760
Oh, yes.

28:34.800 --> 28:36.800
Tell me, are you good with hair?

28:38.040 --> 28:39.680
<font color="#00ffff">I hope so, Ma'am.</font>

28:39.720 --> 28:41.680
I have so much trouble with mine.

28:41.720 --> 28:46.080
Mama always made me wear it like
hers, a l'Anglaise, but...

28:46.120 --> 28:48.520
I would like something
more au courant.

28:49.640 --> 28:53.520
<font color="#00ffff">Au courant, Ma'am?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I am not familiar with that style.</font>

28:53.560 --> 28:55.560
(CHUCKLES)
Oh, no, it's not a hairstyle.

28:55.600 --> 28:58.080
Au courant means fashionable
in French.

28:58.120 --> 29:00.440
I'm inspecting the troops tomorrow

29:00.480 --> 29:03.640
and there'll be so many ladies
of fashion there.

29:04.520 --> 29:06.520
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps a pendant braid</font>
<font color="#00ffff">around each ear?</font>

29:06.560 --> 29:08.600
<font color="#00ffff">It's a style that suits a face</font>
<font color="#00ffff">like yours.</font>

29:10.000 --> 29:11.920
<font color="#00ffff">It is very au courant at the moment.</font>

29:11.960 --> 29:13.640
<font color="#00ff00">Do you think that's wise, Ma'am?</font>

29:13.680 --> 29:15.920
<font color="#00ff00">Miss Skerrett has not done your hair</font>
<font color="#00ff00">before.</font>

29:15.960 --> 29:17.800
<font color="#00ff00">She might not do it to your liking.</font>

29:17.840 --> 29:22.560
Well, if she does my hair half as
well as she has done her own,
I will be quite satisfied.

29:25.240 --> 29:29.320
(SHOUTING)
<font color="#00ff00">The Honourable Lord Hastings.</font>

29:29.360 --> 29:33.200
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen, I am sure,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is a most accomplished young lady,</font>

29:33.240 --> 29:35.440
<font color="#00ffff">but a talent for water colours</font>

29:35.480 --> 29:39.200
<font color="#00ffff">is not going to strike terror into</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the hearts of our enemies.</font>

29:40.800 --> 29:42.920
<font color="#00ff00">The Prime Minister!</font>

29:43.640 --> 29:45.840
<font color="#ffff00">I do not agree with the noble Lord</font>

29:45.880 --> 29:49.160
<font color="#ffff00">that advancing years is the sole</font>
<font color="#ffff00">prerequisite for wisdom.</font>

29:49.200 --> 29:52.560
<font color="#ffff00">I would remind him of his friend,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Pitt the Younger,</font>

29:52.600 --> 29:56.760
<font color="#ffff00">who led this house as prime minister</font>
<font color="#ffff00">at the age of 24.</font>

29:56.800 --> 29:58.560
(SHOUTING)

29:59.880 --> 30:02.560
<font color="#00ff00">HASTINGS: The keen interest</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Prime Minister is taking</font>

30:02.600 --> 30:05.600
<font color="#00ff00">in the young Queen's education</font>
<font color="#00ff00">has not gone unnoticed.</font>

30:05.640 --> 30:07.560
<font color="#00ffff">Melbourne is so attentive to my</font>
<font color="#00ffff">daughter.</font>

30:07.600 --> 30:11.280
There are, apparently,
some women who find him attractive.

30:11.320 --> 30:14.600
<font color="#00ff00">HASTINGS: I'm sure she is most</font>
<font color="#00ff00">appreciative of his support.</font>

30:15.600 --> 30:17.560
(INAUDIBLE)

30:20.440 --> 30:23.320
<font color="#00ffff">Your Majesty,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I wondered if I might have a word.</font>

30:23.360 --> 30:25.640
Now? I need to change for dinner.

30:25.680 --> 30:28.560
<font color="#00ffff">You see, I noticed during the parade</font>

30:28.600 --> 30:32.040
<font color="#00ffff">that you turned your back on the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">troops on a number of occasions.</font>

30:32.080 --> 30:36.040
<font color="#00ffff">I'm sure it was a mistake but,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">according to precedent,</font>

30:36.080 --> 30:38.680
if a sovereign turns their back on a
regiment,

30:38.720 --> 30:41.760
they will no longer form
part of the household cavalry.

30:42.920 --> 30:46.320
<font color="#00ffff">I assume this was not your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">intention. </font><font color="#ffffff"> Indeed not.</font>

30:46.360 --> 30:49.800
But no-one mentioned it to me.
<font color="#00ffff">I assure you they noticed.</font>

30:49.840 --> 30:53.240
But no one likes to correct their
monarch, Ma'am.

30:53.280 --> 30:56.440
Except for you, evidently.
<font color="#00ffff">I feel it is my duty.</font>

30:57.600 --> 31:01.600
<font color="#00ffff">There are many things that the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Baroness, being German, did not</font>
<font color="#00ffff">teach you.</font>

31:01.640 --> 31:03.600
<font color="#00ffff">I'd be happy to help you in future.</font>

31:03.640 --> 31:06.240
<font color="#00ffff">My family have been courtiers for</font>
<font color="#00ffff">generations.</font>

31:07.960 --> 31:11.080
That won't be necessary.
If there are gaps in my knowledge,

31:11.120 --> 31:13.520
I have an excellent tutor
in Lord Melbourne.

31:15.600 --> 31:17.560
<font color="#00ffff">PENGE: The Duchess of Sutherland.</font>

31:17.600 --> 31:20.440
<font color="#00ff00">What a pleasure to be here,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Your Majesty.</font>

31:20.480 --> 31:24.200
<font color="#ffff00">I thought the Duchess would make a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">good choice for Mistress of the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Robes, Ma'am.</font>

31:24.240 --> 31:26.840
And, as you know, the Duke is in the
Cabinet.

31:27.960 --> 31:30.440
She looks very elegant. Is she
respectable?

31:30.480 --> 31:33.520
<font color="#ffff00">As respectable as a great lady can</font>
<font color="#ffff00">be, Ma'am.</font>

31:33.560 --> 31:35.560
<font color="#00ffff">PENGE: The Lady Portman.</font>

31:35.600 --> 31:38.240
<font color="#ffff00">MELBOURNE:</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Now do consider Lady Portman.</font>

31:38.280 --> 31:41.120
<font color="#ffff00">Her husband is Under Secretary for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the Colonies</font>

31:41.160 --> 31:44.240
<font color="#ffff00">and something of a boobie, but she</font>
<font color="#ffff00">knows everyone.</font>

31:46.200 --> 31:48.080
<font color="#ffff00">Lady Portman knew your father,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>

31:48.120 --> 31:51.480
<font color="#00ff00">Such a handsome man, Your Majesty.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">And a very good dancer.</font>

31:51.520 --> 31:54.240
That must explain why I love dancing
so much.

31:54.280 --> 31:57.120
Of course there can be no dancing
until the coronation.

31:57.160 --> 31:59.680
<font color="#00ff00">Is there to be a coronation ball,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Ma'am? </font><font color="#ffffff"> Yes, indeed.</font>

31:59.720 --> 32:01.600
That is if it isn't too expensive,
Lord M?

32:01.640 --> 32:03.760
<font color="#ffff00">I'm hoping you'll only have one</font>
<font color="#ffff00">coronation,</font>

32:03.800 --> 32:05.920
<font color="#ffff00">so I think a little extravagance is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">permitted.</font>

32:10.280 --> 32:12.600
<font color="#00ff00">She seems to be almost besotted.</font>

32:20.040 --> 32:21.640
<font color="#ffff00">Sir John.</font>

32:21.680 --> 32:23.640
<font color="#ffff00">I fear you've been waiting for me.</font>

32:23.680 --> 32:25.360
The Duchess is concerned...

32:26.360 --> 32:28.440
..about the appointment of the
Queen's ladies.

32:28.480 --> 32:30.120
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, I believe it's the first time</font>

32:30.160 --> 32:32.400
<font color="#ffff00">she's been allowed to choose her own</font>
<font color="#ffff00">companions.</font>

32:32.440 --> 32:34.560
<font color="#ffff00">She must find it a pleasant change.</font>

32:39.240 --> 32:42.080
<font color="#00ffff">So you have chosen her</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to be your Mistress of the Robes?</font>

32:42.120 --> 32:44.200
Harriet Sutherland is charming.

32:44.240 --> 32:46.640
<font color="#00ffff">But she is the wife</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of Melbourne's friend.</font>

32:46.680 --> 32:48.800
<font color="#00ffff">It is not good to be</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so in his hands.</font>

32:48.840 --> 32:52.720
<font color="#00ff00">It seems to me you've made her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">into a Whig puppet.</font>

32:52.760 --> 32:54.560
<font color="#ffff00">It may look that way to you,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Sir John.</font>

32:54.600 --> 32:58.440
<font color="#ffff00">As a man who's never seen further</font>
<font color="#ffff00">than his own self-interest,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I suppose it must.</font>

32:58.480 --> 33:00.480
<font color="#ffff00">But I hold myself to a different</font>
<font color="#ffff00">standard.</font>

33:00.520 --> 33:04.640
<font color="#00ffff">I feel I should tell you, Ma'am,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that at Holland House, they call you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Mrs Melbourne.</font>

33:04.680 --> 33:07.160
<font color="#ffff00">MELBOURNE: The Queen is a remarkable</font>
<font color="#ffff00">young woman.</font>

33:07.200 --> 33:10.480
<font color="#ffff00">And I consider it the greatest</font>
<font color="#ffff00">privilege of my career to serve her.</font>

33:10.520 --> 33:14.440
Well, I feel I should tell you that
Mama and Sir John are known as the
Conroyals.

33:14.480 --> 33:16.880
<font color="#00ffff">Sir John, at least, has never been</font>
<font color="#00ffff">involved</font>

33:16.920 --> 33:19.920
in a case of criminal conversation
with a married woman.

33:19.960 --> 33:21.520
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Melbourne was acquitted.</font>

33:21.560 --> 33:24.200
<font color="#00ff00">I cannot look into your soul.</font>

33:24.240 --> 33:28.000
<font color="#ffff00">But you are a man and she is a very</font>
<font color="#ffff00">young and impressionable woman.</font>

33:28.040 --> 33:32.840
<font color="#00ffff">Please, Victoria. He is someone</font>
<font color="#00ffff">who is clever at stealing hearts.</font>

33:32.880 --> 33:34.960
<font color="#00ffff">He must not take yours.</font>

33:37.280 --> 33:38.960
<font color="#ffff00">I bid you good day.</font>

34:07.080 --> 34:09.280
Mama came to see me this morning.

34:11.679 --> 34:12.719
<font color="#ffff00">Yes?</font>

34:12.760 --> 34:15.600
She thinks I should not always be
guided by you.

34:17.199 --> 34:18.960
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps she's right.</font>

34:19.000 --> 34:22.960
What do you mean?
<font color="#ffff00">I should not be your only advisor.</font>

34:23.000 --> 34:24.600
But why not?

34:26.320 --> 34:29.920
<font color="#ffff00">We are...so often in each other's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">company.</font>

34:31.239 --> 34:33.000
<font color="#ffff00">We ride out most days.</font>

34:34.199 --> 34:38.480
<font color="#ffff00">I dine at the palace nearly every</font>
<font color="#ffff00">night. It could be...misconstrued.</font>

34:42.199 --> 34:44.400
I wonder that you have not married
again, Lord M.

34:46.040 --> 34:48.920
<font color="#ffff00">My wife died a few years</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ago and I've...</font>

34:49.800 --> 34:51.760
<font color="#ffff00">..never been able to replace her.</font>

34:51.800 --> 34:57.560
She was not a...model wife by any
means, but she was enough for me.

34:58.680 --> 35:00.800
You did not mind she ran away
with Lord Byron?

35:02.720 --> 35:04.080
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, I minded.</font>

35:05.720 --> 35:07.640
But you did not disown her?

35:09.520 --> 35:11.920
I think I would find such behaviour
hard to forgive.

35:15.800 --> 35:18.080
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps you are too young to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">understand.</font>

35:34.640 --> 35:39.200
<font color="#00ffff">I find it hard to believe that we</font>
<font color="#00ffff">are having this conversation again.</font>

35:39.240 --> 35:43.760
But already this month we've spent
70 guineas on beeswax candles.

35:43.800 --> 35:47.760
<font color="#00ffff">It is a big place, Baroness.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You might even call it a palace.</font>

35:47.800 --> 35:51.320
Well, I'm sorry, Mr Penge,
but you will have to make economies.

35:51.360 --> 35:54.440
<font color="#00ffff">You're not suggesting we use tallow?</font>

35:55.600 --> 35:57.320
If you have to.

36:02.520 --> 36:04.240
<font color="#00ff00">What's wrong with tallow, Mr Penge?</font>

36:04.280 --> 36:08.040
<font color="#00ffff">Nothing, boy, if you enjoy</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the smell of melting mutton fat.</font>

36:12.280 --> 36:14.280
(CARRIAGE WHEELS RATTLE)

36:23.120 --> 36:27.840
<font color="#00ffff">I haven't seen anything so splendid</font>
<font color="#00ffff">since your brother George was here.</font>

36:27.880 --> 36:30.680
<font color="#00ff00">My brother George</font>
<font color="#00ff00">was an extravagant fool.</font>

36:35.600 --> 36:39.000
I suppose I must save the first two
dances for the Grand Duke.

36:39.040 --> 36:41.200
Did you find out how I should
address him?

36:41.240 --> 36:43.200
<font color="#ffff00">Votre Altesse Imperiale.</font>

36:43.240 --> 36:45.160
<font color="#ffff00">The Russians speak French at court.</font>

36:45.200 --> 36:47.880
But is he an Imperial Highness
or a Grand Ducal Highness?

36:47.920 --> 36:50.640
Lord M should be here.
He always knows these things.

36:50.680 --> 36:53.760
<font color="#ffff00">I expect he's on his way, Ma'am.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I thought he'd be here by now!</font>

36:53.800 --> 36:56.240
I don't want to walk in without him.

37:23.920 --> 37:26.640
BUTLER: There is a message
from Lady Portman, My Lord.

37:28.240 --> 37:32.800
She says she knows what day it is,
but the Queen is asking for you.

37:59.920 --> 38:02.600
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, Drina, how charming you look.</font>

38:02.640 --> 38:06.040
<font color="#00ff00">But remember, you're not only here</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to enjoy yourself.</font>

38:06.080 --> 38:10.080
<font color="#00ff00">All the ambassadors will be here,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">plus, of course, the Grand Duke.</font>

38:10.120 --> 38:12.160
<font color="#00ff00">The world will be watching.</font>

38:12.200 --> 38:14.320
<font color="#00ff00">So don't drink too much champagne.</font>

38:14.360 --> 38:16.920
<font color="#00ffff">Or dance too often</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with the same partner.</font>

38:18.360 --> 38:20.280
<font color="#00ffff">Just a little this way.</font>

38:23.040 --> 38:24.720
(BABBLE OF CHATTER)

38:41.280 --> 38:43.920
Where is Lord M?
I expected him hours ago.

38:43.960 --> 38:45.760
<font color="#ffff00">I am sure he'll be here soon, Ma'am.</font>

38:45.800 --> 38:51.720
<font color="#00ffff">His Imperial Highness,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the Grand Duke Alexander of Russia.</font>

39:07.320 --> 39:09.920
Bienvenu.
Nous sommes enchantes de vous voir.

39:09.960 --> 39:12.920
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty, I bring the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">felicitations of my father</font>

39:12.960 --> 39:15.480
<font color="#ffff00">the Emperor on your accession</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the throne.</font>

39:15.520 --> 39:19.160
You speak English!
<font color="#ffff00">Will Your Majesty do me the honour?</font>

39:23.800 --> 39:25.800
# JOHANN STRAUSS: Die Fledermaus

40:07.240 --> 40:11.440
<font color="#00ffff">You have been missed.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">She seems to be managing quite well.</font>

40:15.800 --> 40:17.760
I have been looking for you
everywhere.

40:17.800 --> 40:20.280
You are needed in the retiring room
right away.

40:20.320 --> 40:22.280
All the chamber pots need emptying.

40:22.320 --> 40:24.160
<font color="#00ffff">But that's a chambermaid's job.</font>

40:24.200 --> 40:26.440
I think you can probably manage,
don't you?

40:37.760 --> 40:39.440
<font color="#ffff00">I've been observing all the ladies,</font>

40:39.480 --> 40:41.160
<font color="#ffff00">but none of them dance as</font>
<font color="#ffff00">well as you.</font>

40:41.200 --> 40:44.360
<font color="#ffff00">Please, will you do me the honour?</font>

40:45.520 --> 40:47.160
If you insist.
<font color="#ffff00">I do.</font>

40:56.440 --> 40:58.480
<font color="#00ffff">Are you going to watch her all</font>
<font color="#00ffff">night?</font>

41:02.080 --> 41:04.320
She's completely artless, of course.

41:05.400 --> 41:07.800
She no sooner has a thought
than she expresses it.

41:07.840 --> 41:11.280
<font color="#ffff00">She's too impulsive for a queen,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and yet...</font>

41:23.800 --> 41:26.840
<font color="#00ffff">Can you smell it? The tallow?</font>

41:27.960 --> 41:32.360
Oh, you didn't? What next, Mr Penge?

41:34.160 --> 41:35.680
<font color="#00ff00">Having trouble?</font>

41:42.240 --> 41:45.480
<font color="#00ffff">I had no idea Russians were so</font>
<font color="#00ffff">handsome.</font>

41:45.520 --> 41:48.520
But not civilised.
Look where he's putting his hand!

41:54.320 --> 41:56.560
<font color="#00ffff">(GASPS)</font>
<font color="#ffffff">The poor Queen!</font>

41:59.360 --> 42:04.320
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Alfred, I think it's time the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Grand Duke found another dancing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">partner.</font>

42:12.200 --> 42:14.200
<font color="#00ffff">I beg your pardon, Your Imperial</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Highness,</font>

42:14.240 --> 42:16.000
<font color="#00ffff">there's a messenger from Petersburg.</font>

42:16.040 --> 42:17.520
<font color="#ffff00">Tell him to wait.</font>

42:19.200 --> 42:21.400
<font color="#00ffff">I believe, sir, it is urgent.</font>

42:21.440 --> 42:24.720
<font color="#ffff00">GRAND DUKE: This is outrageous!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Surely this could have waited?</font>

42:32.400 --> 42:34.120
<font color="#ffff00">May I have the honour?</font>

42:43.560 --> 42:48.160
I thought you weren't going to
come. <font color="#ffff00">I had a matter to attend to.</font>

42:48.200 --> 42:51.480
I thought perhaps you were cross
with me. <font color="#ffff00">You?</font>

42:52.760 --> 42:54.360
<font color="#ffff00">Never.</font>

42:54.400 --> 42:57.080
It seems you have been supplanted.

42:58.000 --> 43:01.840
CUMBERLAND: It would be unfortunate
if she were to do anything foolish.

43:02.960 --> 43:05.800
Perhaps you and I can find a way
to prevent that.

43:05.840 --> 43:08.400
<font color="#00ff00">I think we have that situation in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">hand, sir.</font>

43:09.400 --> 43:12.000
I only mean to say, Ma'am,
that should you require it,

43:12.040 --> 43:14.720
you can count on my support.

43:15.920 --> 43:19.800
You dance so well. I wish I could
dance with you every night.

43:22.560 --> 43:24.840
<font color="#ffff00">You are very young.</font>

43:24.880 --> 43:26.360
I am 18!

43:27.160 --> 43:29.400
Old enough to be queen.

43:30.800 --> 43:34.800
You are not old, Lord M.
<font color="#ffff00">If only that were true.</font>

43:34.840 --> 43:36.680
(MUSIC STOPS)

43:36.720 --> 43:38.360
(APPLAUSE)

43:55.000 --> 43:58.840
<font color="#00ffff">I think Lady Flora is with child.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Surely not!</font>

43:58.880 --> 44:00.720
<font color="#00ffff">When she came back from Scotland,</font>

44:00.760 --> 44:02.640
<font color="#00ffff">she shared a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">coach with Conroy alone.</font>

44:02.680 --> 44:04.520
Lady Flora and Sir John!

44:06.560 --> 44:08.800
Right under Mama's nose.

44:14.800 --> 44:16.760
Sir John!

44:16.800 --> 44:18.640
Why aren't you dancing...

44:18.680 --> 44:21.080
with Lady Flora?

44:22.000 --> 44:24.840
I believe she is
your preferred partner.

44:26.760 --> 44:28.960
<font color="#00ff00">You never could take champagne,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Drina.</font>

44:31.880 --> 44:34.160
Ma'am, I did warn you.

44:35.520 --> 44:38.320
Now I suggest you retire
before you embarrass yourself.

44:38.360 --> 44:40.640
You cannot lecture me any more,
Sir John.

44:40.680 --> 44:42.600
I will not listen to you.

44:42.640 --> 44:44.720
And if my mother only knew what you
were like,

44:44.760 --> 44:46.480
she would not listen to you either.

44:49.120 --> 44:50.560
(POLKA PLAYS)

45:05.080 --> 45:08.440
(MUSIC STOPS) <font color="#ffff00">Ma'am, the Duchess</font>
<font color="#ffff00">was hoping for a word.</font>

45:08.480 --> 45:09.920
Mama sent you?

45:11.440 --> 45:13.560
To tell me what to do?
(SILENCE FALLS)

45:18.160 --> 45:19.960
# JOHANN STRAUSS: Wiener Bonbons

45:20.000 --> 45:22.120
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am, it's very hot in here.</font>

45:22.160 --> 45:25.040
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps we should take a walk out on</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the balcony.</font>

45:31.440 --> 45:33.680
I'm afraid you're tired, Ma'am.

45:33.720 --> 45:37.040
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps you should retire.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I don't want to retire.</font>

45:37.080 --> 45:39.360
I want to dance with you.

45:46.680 --> 45:49.000
<font color="#ffff00">Not tonight...</font>

45:50.440 --> 45:51.840
<font color="#ffff00">..Ma'am.</font>

46:27.360 --> 46:29.560
<font color="#00ffff">As you can see, Baroness,</font>

46:29.600 --> 46:33.360
<font color="#00ffff">I'm making an inventory of the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">beeswax candle consumption</font>

46:33.400 --> 46:37.640
<font color="#00ffff">for the palace, so that I can place</font>
<font color="#00ffff">an accurate order for next week.</font>

46:37.680 --> 46:40.560
<font color="#00ffff">We don't want to resort to tallow</font>
<font color="#00ffff">again, do we?</font>

46:40.600 --> 46:43.080
<font color="#ffff00">But what will you do with all those</font>
<font color="#ffff00">candles?</font>

46:43.120 --> 46:45.240
<font color="#ffff00">Some of them are barely touched.</font>

46:45.280 --> 46:47.280
<font color="#ffff00">Surely they can be used again?</font>

46:47.320 --> 46:51.320
<font color="#00ffff">It has always been the custom</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to light fresh tapers</font>

46:51.360 --> 46:53.680
<font color="#00ffff">every evening in the royal</font>
<font color="#00ffff">households.</font>

46:53.720 --> 46:59.160
<font color="#00ffff">To reuse them would require written</font>
<font color="#00ffff">permission from the Lord</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Chamberlain.</font>

47:03.720 --> 47:07.800
<font color="#ffff00">Well, the sooner the gas lighting</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is installed the better.</font>

47:12.480 --> 47:15.160
Written permission from the Lord
Chamberlain.

47:15.200 --> 47:17.280
Whatever will you say next, Mr Penge?

47:17.320 --> 47:21.160
<font color="#00ffff">Gas lighting.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">She said gas lighting. </font><font color="#ffffff"> Yes.</font>

47:21.200 --> 47:23.400
You'll need to find a new perk.

47:24.640 --> 47:26.240
Hm?

47:26.280 --> 47:27.920
(BARKS)
Fetch it, Dash.

47:28.720 --> 47:31.640
<font color="#00ffff">Drina, you wanted to see me?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Mama.</font>

47:31.680 --> 47:33.240
(CLEARS THROAT)

47:33.960 --> 47:36.520
You must send Lady Flora
and Sir John away immediately.

47:36.560 --> 47:38.240
I do not want them here.

47:38.280 --> 47:40.480
I certainly do not want them at the
coronation.

47:41.640 --> 47:44.080
<font color="#00ffff">Du willst was?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Speak English, Mama!</font>

47:44.120 --> 47:46.720
<font color="#00ffff">I don't understand, Drina!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(BARKS)</font>

47:46.760 --> 47:48.480
Mama.

47:50.680 --> 47:55.440
I'm sorry, but I believe there's
been a criminal conversation between
them.

47:55.480 --> 47:58.160
Surely you have noticed
Lady Flora is with child?

47:58.200 --> 48:01.480
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, Drina! It is impossible.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">No, it is quite possible.</font>

48:01.520 --> 48:05.360
Lady Flora and Sir John shared a
carriage from Scotland alone.

48:05.400 --> 48:08.080
<font color="#00ffff">(SCOFFS) Who told you that?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Lehzen.</font>

48:08.960 --> 48:10.640
<font color="#00ffff">Baroness Lehzen knows so much about</font>

48:10.680 --> 48:12.480
<font color="#00ffff">what happens between a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">man and a woman?</font>

48:12.520 --> 48:16.040
Mama! That man has controlled you
and now he has betrayed you!

48:16.080 --> 48:17.920
<font color="#00ffff">Ah!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Mama!</font>

48:17.960 --> 48:19.760
(VASE SMASHES)

48:22.840 --> 48:24.440
(DOOR CLOSES)

48:24.480 --> 48:26.320
(APPROACHING FOOTSTEPS)

48:26.360 --> 48:29.200
<font color="#00ff00">Ah, Lady Flora, I was hoping I might</font>
<font color="#00ff00">find you.</font>

48:30.040 --> 48:32.040
<font color="#00ff00">It seems hardly credible</font>

48:32.080 --> 48:34.360
<font color="#00ff00">but I've had no card for the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">coronation.</font>

48:34.400 --> 48:39.320
<font color="#ffff00">Neither have I. </font><font color="#00ff00"> Well, it's</font>
<font color="#00ff00">an insult to the </font><font color="#00ff00"> Duchess,</font>

48:39.360 --> 48:41.320
<font color="#00ff00">not to invite her closest</font>
<font color="#00ff00">companions.</font>

48:41.360 --> 48:44.600
<font color="#ffff00">I am no longer surprised</font>
<font color="#ffff00">by the Queen's behaviour.</font>

48:44.640 --> 48:47.080
<font color="#ffff00">She seems to have lost</font>
<font color="#ffff00">all sense of decorum.</font>

48:50.280 --> 48:53.840
<font color="#ffff00">Lady Flora has powerful friends,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am. Tory friends.</font>

48:54.480 --> 48:58.920
<font color="#ffff00">It would be unfortunate to have a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">scandal so close to the coronation.</font>

48:58.960 --> 49:03.200
<font color="#ffff00">There are those who believe a girl</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as young as you is not capable of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">being queen.</font>

49:03.240 --> 49:05.080
That's what Conroy believes.

49:05.120 --> 49:07.240
A man of the basest character.
He must go.

49:07.280 --> 49:09.480
<font color="#ffff00">There may be more delicate ways</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of making him go</font>

49:09.520 --> 49:13.200
<font color="#ffff00">than accusing him of getting a child</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on Lady Flora. </font><font color="#ffffff"> Even if it's true?</font>

49:15.200 --> 49:17.880
<font color="#ffff00">I have no desire to stir up the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Tories at the moment.</font>

49:17.920 --> 49:21.880
<font color="#ffff00">It's hard enough controlling my own</font>
<font color="#ffff00">party. But I don't want you to do</font>
<font color="#ffff00">something rash.</font>

49:21.920 --> 49:24.520
I believe I have a duty here to find
out the truth.

49:24.560 --> 49:28.640
<font color="#ffff00">I'm afraid the truth is vastly</font>
<font color="#ffff00">overrated. Much better if you can</font>
<font color="#ffff00">let this affair alone.</font>

49:29.760 --> 49:31.800
Tomorrow I take the coronation oath.

49:33.760 --> 49:38.240
How can I promise to serve my
country faithfully when my court is
rank with corruption?

49:38.280 --> 49:42.840
<font color="#ffff00">The problem with a scandal is that</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the mud does not always stick to the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">right people.</font>

49:42.880 --> 49:45.960
Is that all you care about, avoiding
a scandal?

49:48.280 --> 49:51.840
<font color="#ffff00">I do know how painful and</font>
<font color="#ffff00">humiliating a scandal can be.</font>

49:53.560 --> 49:56.160
<font color="#00ffff">I don't believe I sent for you,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Sir James. </font><font color="#ffffff"> No.</font>

49:56.200 --> 49:59.720
No, I...I... <font color="#ffff00">I believe I know why</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you are here, Sir James,</font>

49:59.760 --> 50:02.880
and you may tell the Queen
that I have nothing to say.

50:04.480 --> 50:06.120
SIR JAMES: I am afraid, Lady Flora,

50:06.160 --> 50:08.120
the Queen will not be
satisfied with that.

50:08.160 --> 50:10.480
<font color="#00ffff">DUCHESS OF KENT:</font>
<font color="#00ffff">What does my daughter want?</font>

50:10.520 --> 50:12.880
I believe, Ma'am,

50:12.920 --> 50:16.520
she would like an...examination.

50:17.520 --> 50:19.440
For the avoidance of doubt.

50:20.280 --> 50:24.560
The Queen feels it is the only way
to put the matter to rest.

50:26.680 --> 50:30.520
<font color="#ffff00">There are two things I hold dear in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">life, Sir James.</font>

50:31.160 --> 50:34.480
<font color="#ffff00">One is my church and the other is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the crown.</font>

50:34.520 --> 50:39.440
If the Queen really believes that I
am capable of betraying everything
that I hold dear...

50:41.160 --> 50:43.480
..then I am willing to prove her
wrong.

50:45.040 --> 50:48.360
<font color="#ffff00">But I want my own physician to be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">present as well.</font>

50:48.400 --> 50:50.960
<font color="#ffff00">For the avoidance of doubt.</font>

50:53.320 --> 50:57.280
<font color="#00ffff">Flora is so distressed</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that it has made her quite unwell.</font>

50:58.520 --> 51:01.280
<font color="#00ff00">Your daughter has always been</font>
<font color="#00ff00">unstable.</font>

51:02.320 --> 51:06.200
That is why we wanted a regency
for the good of the country.

51:06.240 --> 51:10.320
<font color="#00ff00">Well, now...now people will see</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that we were right.</font>

51:12.080 --> 51:13.720
SOLDIER: Fire!

51:50.800 --> 51:54.120
I solemnly promise...
(DOOR OPENS)

51:58.560 --> 52:03.160
<font color="#00ffff">Majesty, it is still so early.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You should rest.</font>

52:03.200 --> 52:04.880
I can't sleep any longer.

52:11.240 --> 52:13.240
(DISTANT SHOUTING)

52:14.280 --> 52:16.000
Can you hear them?

52:18.560 --> 52:20.240
I am ready.

52:23.200 --> 52:25.200
(CHEERING)

52:28.800 --> 52:30.800
# Gloriana

52:35.080 --> 52:37.080
# Hallelujah

52:41.680 --> 52:43.920
# Gloriana

52:55.120 --> 52:57.720
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)
<font color="#ffff00">Enter.</font>

53:39.520 --> 53:41.520
# Gloria

53:45.480 --> 53:47.480
# Hallelujah

53:52.440 --> 53:54.440
# Gloria

53:57.800 --> 53:58.920
# Hallelujah

53:58.960 --> 54:00.960
ALL: God save the Queen!

54:02.560 --> 54:04.160
God save the Queen!

54:04.960 --> 54:06.440
God save the Queen!

54:22.840 --> 54:25.320
(CHEERING, BELLS CHIME)

54:30.720 --> 54:31.920
Dash?

54:34.160 --> 54:36.160
(WHIMPERS)
Come on.

54:37.480 --> 54:39.480
(WHIMPERS)

54:40.640 --> 54:42.680
<font color="#ffff00">Ma'am.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(DASH BARKS)</font>

54:43.640 --> 54:46.960
<font color="#ffff00">I wanted to congratulate you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on your performance today.</font>

54:47.000 --> 54:49.120
<font color="#ffff00">You were most regal.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(DOOR OPENS)</font>

54:49.160 --> 54:50.440
<font color="#00ffff">PENGE: Sir James Clark.</font>

54:50.480 --> 54:54.120
<font color="#ffff00">Forgive me, Ma'am, I thought it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">better that I come in person.</font>

54:54.160 --> 55:00.360
<font color="#ffff00">I have performed an...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">examination of Lady Flora</font>

55:00.400 --> 55:03.120
<font color="#ffff00">and I have found her to be virgo</font>
<font color="#ffff00">intacta.</font>

55:04.800 --> 55:08.600
But is she with child?
<font color="#ffff00">Er...no, Ma'am.</font>

55:09.760 --> 55:12.200
The one generally precludes the
other.

55:13.800 --> 55:15.280
Oh, I see.

55:15.320 --> 55:18.360
<font color="#ffff00">I believe that the swelling,</font>

55:18.400 --> 55:22.000
<font color="#ffff00">which indeed could be mistaken for a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">pregnancy,</font>

55:22.040 --> 55:25.160
<font color="#ffff00">is actually the result of a tumour.</font>

55:26.040 --> 55:30.120
<font color="#ffff00">I believe Lady Flora</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to be gravely ill.</font>

55:39.760 --> 55:42.080
<font color="#00ffff">Conroy.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Sir.</font>

55:42.120 --> 55:43.600
<font color="#00ffff">How is Lady Flora?</font>

55:44.480 --> 55:46.720
<font color="#00ff00">She's er... She's very weak, sir.</font>

55:46.760 --> 55:49.480
<font color="#00ff00">She's refusing all food.</font>

55:50.400 --> 55:52.760
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen must be brought to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">account.</font>

55:52.800 --> 55:55.760
<font color="#00ffff">She has treated Lady Flora quite</font>
<font color="#00ffff">shamefully.</font>

55:57.000 --> 55:59.520
<font color="#00ff00">You know about the examination?</font>

55:59.560 --> 56:02.920
<font color="#00ffff">Lord Hastings is an old friend</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and fellow Tory.</font>

56:02.960 --> 56:06.280
<font color="#00ffff">He feels very strongly about the way</font>
<font color="#00ffff">his sister has been treated.</font>

56:07.280 --> 56:09.280
<font color="#00ff00">I think the public would be shocked</font>

56:09.320 --> 56:11.520
<font color="#00ff00">if they knew of the Queen's part</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in this.</font>

56:11.560 --> 56:15.960
<font color="#00ffff">My niece must not be allowed</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to bring the crown into disrepute.</font>

56:17.200 --> 56:20.320
<font color="#00ff00">The Duchess feels that it</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is time Victoria</font>

56:20.360 --> 56:23.120
<font color="#00ff00">received a more formal guidance.</font>

56:24.200 --> 56:27.800
<font color="#00ffff">A regency? </font><font color="#00ff00"> I believe it has come to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that, yes.</font>

56:38.360 --> 56:41.440
VENDOR:
Latest, Lady Flora's distress.

56:41.480 --> 56:44.440
Come and see Lady Flora's distress...

56:44.480 --> 56:47.480
<font color="#00ffff">HASTINGS: This shocking mistreatment</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of an innocent woman</font>

56:47.520 --> 56:49.760
does not reflect well on our new
monarch.

56:49.800 --> 56:52.720
<font color="#00ffff">Should our queen not be guided by a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">regent,</font>

56:52.760 --> 56:57.040
<font color="#00ffff">someone older and wiser who will not</font>
<font color="#00ffff">lead the country into disrepute?</font>

56:57.080 --> 57:03.040
<font color="#00ffff">And forgive us our trespasses...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">And those who trespass against us.</font>

57:03.080 --> 57:05.400
<font color="#00ffff">Melbourne, just the fellow I was</font>
<font color="#00ffff">looking for.</font>

57:05.440 --> 57:07.320
<font color="#ffff00">I'm on my way to the palace.</font>

57:07.360 --> 57:10.960
<font color="#00ffff">It's unfortunate that this business</font>
<font color="#00ffff">has got into the papers.</font>

57:11.720 --> 57:14.160
<font color="#00ffff">My niece has been queen</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for five minutes</font>

57:14.200 --> 57:16.960
<font color="#00ffff">and already the crown</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is covered in scandal.</font>

57:17.000 --> 57:21.840
<font color="#00ff00">Good morning, Ma'am.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I suppose...you've seen this?</font>

57:21.880 --> 57:26.240
<font color="#ffff00">A firm hand on the tiller.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">That's what this country needs.</font>

57:26.280 --> 57:28.560
<font color="#ffff00">MELBOURNE: And would that hand be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your own, sir?</font>

57:28.600 --> 57:32.320
<font color="#00ffff">CUMBERLAND: The press can be so</font>
<font color="#00ffff">cruel. It seems the obvious choice.</font>

57:32.360 --> 57:34.600
<font color="#ffff00">MELBOURNE: But not the popular one,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I think.</font>

57:34.640 --> 57:36.360
<font color="#ffff00">The Queen may have her difficulties,</font>

57:36.400 --> 57:38.520
<font color="#ffff00">but what would rally the public to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">her support</font>

57:38.560 --> 57:40.600
would be the prospect of being ruled
by you.

57:49.240 --> 57:51.120
<font color="#ffff00">Might I have a word with you, Ma'am?</font>

57:57.640 --> 58:00.040
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry, Ma'am,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm afraid it couldn't wait.</font>

58:00.080 --> 58:02.480
<font color="#ffff00">Flora Hastings has taken a turn for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the worse.</font>

58:07.760 --> 58:10.280
I should have listened
when you told me to do nothing.

58:10.320 --> 58:13.520
It's always easier to give advice
than it is to follow it, Ma'am.

58:16.440 --> 58:19.200
(EXHALES) I'm afraid.

58:19.240 --> 58:23.640
<font color="#ffff00">I know, Ma'am, but I also know how</font>
<font color="#ffff00">much courage you have.</font>

58:27.360 --> 58:29.040
Lady Flora.

58:30.320 --> 58:32.040
I'm sorry to see you so unwell,

58:32.080 --> 58:36.080
but I'm sure with rest and care
you'll soon be on your feet again.

58:42.760 --> 58:44.240
(DOOR CLOSES)

58:46.760 --> 58:48.760
Is there anything we can send you?

58:48.800 --> 58:51.160
Some peaches perhaps?

58:51.200 --> 58:54.240
I am beyond peaches, Ma'am.

58:54.280 --> 58:56.920
You mustn't say that, Lady Flora.
With rest and care...

58:56.960 --> 58:59.600
Everything I need is here.

58:59.640 --> 59:02.360
I know I am going to a better place.

59:06.720 --> 59:08.320
I have...

59:09.560 --> 59:12.280
I have wronged you, Lady Flora.

59:14.120 --> 59:16.440
And now I've come to ask
for your forgiveness.

59:16.480 --> 59:18.640
<font color="#ffff00">Only God can forgive you.</font>

59:21.800 --> 59:24.720
I was wrong. I see that now.

59:25.920 --> 59:29.800
<font color="#ffff00">You did not act like a queen.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I thought it was my duty.</font>

59:30.560 --> 59:36.240
<font color="#ffff00">To be a queen, you must be more</font>
<font color="#ffff00">than a little girl with a crown.</font>

59:36.280 --> 59:39.600
You have responsibility for your
subjects.

59:39.640 --> 59:42.800
They are not dolls to be played
with.

59:44.400 --> 59:46.280
(LABOURED BREATHING)

59:58.440 --> 01:00:02.800
<font color="#00ffff">It won't be long now.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">First death of the palace.</font>

01:00:05.680 --> 01:00:07.720
I wonder if we'll go into mourning.

01:00:08.600 --> 01:00:10.320
If only the Queen had asked me,

01:00:10.360 --> 01:00:12.800
I could have told her that Lady
Flora was blameless.

01:00:14.360 --> 01:00:16.080
I have a nose for these things.

01:00:17.960 --> 01:00:21.560
<font color="#ffff00">Look what I found on my daily</font>
<font color="#ffff00">inspection.</font>

01:00:21.600 --> 01:00:26.160
<font color="#ffff00">A parcel of the Queen's gloves on</font>
<font color="#ffff00">their way to what I believe is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">called "the pickers",</font>

01:00:26.200 --> 01:00:27.560
<font color="#ffff00">to be sold at a profit.</font>

01:00:29.840 --> 01:00:32.800
<font color="#ffff00">Mrs Jenkins.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

01:00:32.840 --> 01:00:35.120
<font color="#ffff00">I think I recognise</font>
<font color="#ffff00">this as your hand.</font>

01:00:39.320 --> 01:00:42.480
<font color="#00ffff">No, Baroness, that is my writing.</font>

01:00:45.880 --> 01:00:47.920
<font color="#ffff00">I expected more from you,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Miss Skerrett.</font>

01:00:47.960 --> 01:00:49.840
<font color="#ffff00">I shall have to tell the Queen.</font>

01:00:53.920 --> 01:00:55.480
(DOOR CLOSES)

01:00:55.520 --> 01:00:59.160
<font color="#00ff00">What did you that for? Mrs Jenkins</font>
<font color="#00ff00">has been no friend to you.</font>

01:00:59.200 --> 01:01:01.480
<font color="#00ffff">Do as you would be done by,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Brodie.</font>

01:01:09.360 --> 01:01:10.720
(FOOTSTEPS)

01:01:11.680 --> 01:01:14.720
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, forgive me, Majesty.</font>

01:01:16.440 --> 01:01:18.720
No, that's all right.

01:01:18.760 --> 01:01:21.560
<font color="#ffff00">There is a concern about your new</font>
<font color="#ffff00">dresser.</font>

01:01:21.600 --> 01:01:24.000
<font color="#ffff00">There is evidence</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that she may be less than honest.</font>

01:01:27.360 --> 01:01:30.360
Baroness Lehzen tells me
that I should dismiss you.

01:01:32.000 --> 01:01:34.360
<font color="#ffff00">You must answer Her Majesty.</font>

01:01:39.720 --> 01:01:42.360
I've abused my position, Ma'am.

01:01:42.400 --> 01:01:44.880
<font color="#00ffff">I've been selling your gloves to the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">pickers.</font>

01:01:52.360 --> 01:01:55.240
You mean there are people
who buy my old gloves?

01:02:01.440 --> 01:02:03.280
But after all, I don't need them.

01:02:03.320 --> 01:02:05.200
Why shouldn't you sell them?

01:02:05.240 --> 01:02:07.680
<font color="#ffff00">But Majesty, it is a matter of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">principle.</font>

01:02:07.720 --> 01:02:10.120
I've had enough of principles.

01:02:11.400 --> 01:02:12.800
Skerrett can stay.

01:02:12.840 --> 01:02:14.600
Thank you, Ma'am.

01:02:25.320 --> 01:02:28.080
<font color="#00ffff">My... My poor Flora is dead.</font>

01:02:32.560 --> 01:02:35.040
Oh, Mama, I am sorry.

01:02:35.080 --> 01:02:37.960
<font color="#00ffff">So you should be.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You drove her to her grave.</font>

01:02:40.120 --> 01:02:41.640
<font color="#ffff00">Excuse me, Ma'am.</font>

01:02:49.320 --> 01:02:51.960
I went to see Lady Flora to
apologise.

01:02:53.400 --> 01:02:56.000
<font color="#ffff00">You sent doctors to humiliate a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">dying woman.</font>

01:02:57.680 --> 01:02:59.560
I am sorry, Mama.

01:03:01.000 --> 01:03:02.560
I see now I was mistaken.

01:03:02.600 --> 01:03:04.840
<font color="#ffff00">It is Sir John you should be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">apologising to.</font>

01:03:04.880 --> 01:03:07.360
He also has been accused
and he too is innocent.

01:03:07.400 --> 01:03:09.200
Of that particular crime perhaps.

01:03:10.040 --> 01:03:12.600
But he is guilty, Mama, of far
worse.

01:03:13.600 --> 01:03:16.080
Do you think I am blind?
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, Drina.</font>

01:03:16.120 --> 01:03:18.360
You have always said you wanted to
protect me

01:03:18.400 --> 01:03:20.480
but you have never protected me
from him.

01:03:20.520 --> 01:03:24.840
Every time he laughed at me for
being short, you laughed with him.

01:03:24.880 --> 01:03:28.560
Every time he told me I was young
and foolish, you agreed.

01:03:29.960 --> 01:03:31.800
But then, ever since I can remember,

01:03:31.840 --> 01:03:34.120
you have always looked at him first,
then me.

01:03:34.160 --> 01:03:37.280
<font color="#00ffff">My poor Drina.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You are not yourself.</font>

01:03:37.320 --> 01:03:40.360
<font color="#00ffff">You cannot continue like this.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Enough!</font>

01:03:40.400 --> 01:03:42.080
Enough, Mama!

01:03:47.400 --> 01:03:49.120
You may leave us.

01:04:16.280 --> 01:04:18.600
I suppose I should say thank you.

01:04:18.640 --> 01:04:20.320
<font color="#00ffff">No need.</font>

01:04:21.640 --> 01:04:23.880
So long as we understand each other.

01:04:27.000 --> 01:04:28.800
You are a strange one,
Miss Skerrett.

01:04:31.520 --> 01:04:33.560
I thank you all the same.

01:04:42.320 --> 01:04:44.320
(FOOTSTEPS)

01:04:46.640 --> 01:04:48.200
<font color="#ffff00">Good morning, Ma'am.</font>

01:04:51.760 --> 01:04:54.800
<font color="#ffff00">Come. There are three regiments</font>
<font color="#ffff00">waiting, I believe.</font>

01:04:57.320 --> 01:04:58.520
I can't.

01:05:02.400 --> 01:05:04.200
I can't do it.

01:05:07.200 --> 01:05:09.200
Everything is ruined.

01:05:11.200 --> 01:05:13.040
It's all my fault.

01:05:27.160 --> 01:05:29.440
<font color="#ffff00">I don't believe I ever told you...</font>

01:05:29.480 --> 01:05:31.960
<font color="#ffff00">why I was late for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the coronation ball.</font>

01:05:34.960 --> 01:05:36.960
<font color="#ffff00">Did you know I had a son?</font>

01:05:39.440 --> 01:05:41.240
<font color="#ffff00">Augustus.</font>

01:05:43.120 --> 01:05:45.720
And that day was his birthday.

01:05:48.960 --> 01:05:52.440
<font color="#ffff00">When Caro ran away,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he became very afraid of the dark.</font>

01:05:53.920 --> 01:05:57.600
<font color="#ffff00">He would only go to sleep</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if I was...holding his hand.</font>

01:06:00.400 --> 01:06:04.760
<font color="#ffff00">Funny thing is, I don't think I was</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ever happier than on those nights</font>
<font color="#ffff00">when I was sitting there...</font>

01:06:06.240 --> 01:06:08.160
<font color="#ffff00">..feeling my little boy drift off.</font>

01:06:09.720 --> 01:06:14.160
<font color="#ffff00">When he died, I thought there was no</font>
<font color="#ffff00">point to my existence.</font>

01:06:14.200 --> 01:06:17.600
Lord M, how can you say that?
<font color="#ffff00">I no longer feel that way, Ma'am.</font>

01:06:19.680 --> 01:06:23.560
<font color="#ffff00">I thought I would never find any</font>
<font color="#ffff00">solace.</font>

01:06:24.360 --> 01:06:27.720
<font color="#ffff00">But then I became</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your prime minister</font>

01:06:27.760 --> 01:06:32.040
<font color="#ffff00">and I think... I hope, your friend.</font>

01:06:34.200 --> 01:06:37.360
Of course, nothing will ever bring
my boy back,

01:06:38.200 --> 01:06:41.960
<font color="#ffff00">but through you I've been given a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">reason to continue.</font>

01:06:44.800 --> 01:06:47.200
And you must do the same.

01:06:47.240 --> 01:06:49.240
<font color="#ffff00">You must go out and you must smile.</font>

01:06:50.680 --> 01:06:52.640
<font color="#ffff00">You must smile and wave,</font>

01:06:53.720 --> 01:06:56.800
<font color="#ffff00">and never let them know how hard it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is to bear.</font>

01:07:03.760 --> 01:07:05.720
MAN: God bless the Duchess!

01:07:06.840 --> 01:07:09.640
<font color="#ffff00">MAN: Long live the Duchess!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(CHEERING)</font>

01:07:09.680 --> 01:07:12.040
(HORSE WHINNIES)

01:07:32.000 --> 01:07:34.360
<font color="#00ff00">MAN: What about Flora Hastings?</font>

01:07:36.080 --> 01:07:37.800
<font color="#00ff00">Shame on Her Majesty!</font>

01:07:39.040 --> 01:07:40.960
<font color="#ffff00">MAN: What about Lady Flora?</font>

01:08:21.720 --> 01:08:25.520
VICTORIA: I followed your advice as
far as I was able.

01:08:26.560 --> 01:08:29.640
I waved, although I couldn't smile.

01:08:31.120 --> 01:08:33.760
But I feel I shall smile in the
future...

01:08:33.800 --> 01:08:36.279
with your help...

01:08:37.600 --> 01:08:38.960
..Lord M.

01:08:40.000 --> 01:08:41.720
<font color="#ffff00">BRODIE: Your boxes, Ma'am.</font>

