01:09:17.439 --> 01:09:20.640
<font color="#00ff00">I'm afraid the strain of her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">position has disordered her senses.</font>

01:09:20.680 --> 01:09:23.439
<font color="#ffff00">So young and with such</font>
<font color="#ffff00">responsibilities.</font>

01:09:23.479 --> 01:09:25.240
Oh, Mama...

01:09:25.279 --> 01:09:27.880
<font color="#00ffff">She seems to have lost</font>
<font color="#00ffff">all sense of propriety.</font>

01:09:27.920 --> 01:09:31.439
<font color="#ffff00">You understand what is at stake?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Lord Melbourne, you forget yourself!</font>

01:09:31.479 --> 01:09:34.160
<font color="#00ff00">You suggesting the Queen is not of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">sound mind, sir?</font>

01:09:34.200 --> 01:09:36.080
(SCREAMS)
<font color="#ffff00">Calm yourself!</font>

01:09:36.160 --> 01:09:37.720
Oh! <font color="#00ffff">Oh!</font>

01:09:37.760 --> 01:09:39.399
Could we have met before?

01:09:39.439 --> 01:09:42.920
<font color="#00ffff">Even if Melbourne scrapes through,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I don't think he'll carry on.</font>

01:09:42.960 --> 01:09:45.200
<font color="#ffff00">I can no longer lead the Whigs in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">government.</font>

01:09:45.240 --> 01:09:47.399
You really mean to forsake me?

